:: morning routine {"position":"700,400","size":"100,100"}
The alarm goes off at 6:15.
You let it ring for the full minute before you reach over and kill it.

Skyler's side of the bed is already empty. She sleeps lighter since the pregnancy.

You lie there and take inventory.
The chemo is making your gums ache.
Your jaw, your left shoulder, the place on your back where the port sits under the skin.

You are Walter Hartwell White, 50 years old, high school chemistry teacher, and the producer of the purest methamphetamine the DEA has ever catalogued.

All this, and it's time to get up for the day.

[[Get up]]
[[Just five more minutes]]


:: Just five more minutes {"position":"550,525","size":"100,100"}
You close your eyes.
(click: ?page)[==
Five minutes is a lie you tell yourself so you can stay under the covers without admitting you are hiding.
(click: ?page)[==
You are hiding.
(click: ?page)[==
From the mirror. From Skyler. From the phone that is going to ring today and tell you something you do not want to hear.
(click: ?page)[==
Get up, Walter.

[[Get up]]


:: Get up {"position":"700,525","size":"100,100"}
You swing your legs over the edge of the bed.

The floor is cold. That helps.

[[Shower]]


:: Shower {"position":"700,650","size":"100,100"}
Hot water on the back of your neck.
(click: ?page)[==
You think about the cook schedule.
(click: ?page)[==
You think about Jesse. Jesse has been slipping. Jesse has been high at every meet for the last three weeks.
(click: ?page)[==
Jesse and that girl.
(click: ?page)[==
Jane.
(click: ?page)[==
You have not said her name out loud in days and you realize, standing here under the water, that this is deliberate.
(click: ?page)[==
Naming a thing makes it real. Makes it something you have to deal with.

[[Downstairs]]


:: Downstairs {"position":"700,775","size":"100,100"}
Skyler is at the counter with a glass of orange juice and the classifieds open in front of her.

"Morning."

"Morning."

She does not look up.

<div style="text-align:center; margin:20px 0;">
  <img src="images/skyler-kitchen.jpg"
